{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 310821, "create_time": 1658659049, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我觉得不合理", "timestamp": 1658659049}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 310825, "create_time": 1658659138, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "洞主要不问问河北除了衡水的同学？", "timestamp": 1658659138}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 310838, "create_time": 1658659379, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re : 可以了解一下山东高中教育现状", "timestamp": 1658659379}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 310845, "create_time": 1658659658, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 山东高中比较均衡吧", "timestamp": 1658659658}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 310846, "create_time": 1658659690, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 没有过于强势的高中", "timestamp": 1658659690}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 310852, "create_time": 1658659864, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 河北的超级中学就是衡水和石二了吧，不知道衡水现在还面向全省招生吗，不面向全省的话也很难保持之前的成绩了吧", "timestamp": 1658659864}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 310873, "create_time": 1658660909, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "有得有失吧，cz没法去省里超级中学，没能在竞赛上拿好成绩，没能经历素质教育，上了大学眼界能力啥的感觉不太够，不过当小镇做题家也还行，和一起长大的同学们相处的生活很美好，高考成绩也是顶尖的。", "timestamp": 1658660909}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 310878, "create_time": 1658661013, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "要是当初被禁了Eve就估计看不见这条洞了", "timestamp": 1658661013}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 310885, "create_time": 1658661403, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "反转了，我就在有超级中学的城市", "timestamp": 1658661403}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311012, "create_time": 1658667339, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "cz湖北，华师一或许也算超级中学吧，有在全省招生。但并没有对各地高中造成严重的生源流失，也没有像河北一样内卷。感觉一是因为招生名额很少，二是只能通过专门考试优录，不能通过中考。所以cz对这种全省招生不反感，因为保持了极大的克制，但真的不支持衡水的那种全省招生。", "timestamp": 1658667339}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311056, "create_time": 1658669727, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "深中之前这么多年一直只在深圳招生（虽说现在也有一个班开放全省招生了），但清北人数依然逐年上涨。当然这和广东本身分数线就低也有关系，而且深中的清北人数多也只是在广东省内算多的。", "timestamp": 1658669727}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311059, "create_time": 1658669917, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "现在还没禁吗？什么蛮夷之地", "timestamp": 1658669917}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311637, "create_time": 1658709207, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "长痛不如短痛", "timestamp": 1658709207}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312023, "create_time": 1658727077, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "Re Grace: 上个月回华一，老师说明年开始全省缩招到300，也是变相削弱了", "timestamp": 1658727077}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312177, "create_time": 1658733977, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 12, "text": "支持超级中学全省招生，大力反对教育机会不均等", "timestamp": 1658733977}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312704, "create_time": 1658754994, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "所以超级中学全省招生是促进还是违背教育公平呢", "timestamp": 1658754994}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312964, "create_time": 1658763352, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 禁止超级中学从全省招生相当于只准清北招北京学生吧", "timestamp": 1658763352}], "create_time": 1658658163, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1658763352, "likenum": 12, "n_attentions": 12, "n_comments": 17, "pid": 87938, "poll": null, "reply": 17, "text": "禁止超级中学从全省招生的政策合理吗？一方面这能改善很多地方高中多年无清北，成绩不断下滑的现状,之前很多地方的前几名全都出去了，地方高中很难j教出成绩。但从另一方面来讲，地方的顶尖学生就无法获得更优质的教育资源，包括竞赛资源，自招资格，以及和更优秀的同学一起学习等等。", "timestamp": 1658658163}}